Mary Schapiro - Wikipedia






















 






Mary Schapiro

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Mary Schapiro








29th Chairwoman of the Securities and Exchange Commission


In office
January 27, 2009 – December 14, 2012


